OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782150512
OL,3,CGreens name councillor as candidate to
OL,4,Creplace Burnham as Manchester mayor
OL,6,FThe Green Party has announced
OL,7,Fcouncillor Geraldine Coggins as its
OL,8,Fcandidate in the by-election for the
OL,9,FGreater Manchester mayoralty triggered
OL,10,Fby Andy Burnham's election as an MP.
OL,12,FLabour is pitching the contest as a
OL,13,Ftwo-horse race between Labour and
OL,14,FReform UK, but the Greens are looking
OL,15,Fto build on their success in the
OL,16,FGorton and Denton by-election with a
OL,17,Fstrong challenge of their own.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
