PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782150512
OL,3,CGreens name councillor as candidate to
OL,4,Creplace Burnham as Manchester mayor
OL,6,FCllr Coggins told supporters at a
OL,7,Flaunch event in Manchester that it was
OL,8,Fa straight contest between the Greens
OL,9,Fand Nigel Farage's party as she
OL,10,Fpledged to improve transport, housing
OL,11,Fand choose "people and planet over
OL,12,Fprofits".
OL,14,FThe candidate, a councillor for
OL,15,FAlrincham in Trafford since 2018, is
OL,16,Foriginally from Ireland, and a
OL,17,Fpublished academic with a background
OL,18,Fin leadership, public finance and
OL,19,Fstrategic decision-making, the party
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,26,@sD@LOUtD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
