PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782150512
OL,3,CGreens name councillor as candidate to
OL,4,Creplace Burnham as Manchester mayor
OL,6,FParty leader Zack Polanski said she
OL,7,Fwould focus on affordable social and
OL,8,Fcouncil housing and lobby the national
OL,9,Fgovernment for rent controls.
OL,11,FCllr Coggins drew parallels to the
OL,12,FGorton and Denton by-election that saw
OL,13,FHannah Spencer become a Green MP
OL,14,Fearlier this year.
OL,16,FMs Spencer was the Greens' previous
OL,17,Fmayoral candidate two years ago, and
OL,18,Fcame fifth with 6.9% of the vote, but
OL,19,Fthe new candidate says things have
OL,20,Fchanged since then.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782150512
OL,3,CGreens name councillor as candidate to
OL,4,Creplace Burnham as Manchester mayor
OL,6,F"We know that things have changed, the
OL,7,Fpeople now know the Greens can win,
OL,8,Fand I think it's really important that
OL,9,Fpeople know in this election this is a
OL,10,Fstraight race between our green
OL,11,Fmessage of hope and unity and the
OL,12,Ftoxic divisive politics of Reform, so
OL,13,Fyou can vote green with your head and
OL,14,Fyour heart," Cllr Coggins said.
OL,16,FLabour's losses in the May local
OL,17,Felections were "existential" and a
OL,18,FReform mayor would be a "disaster" for
OL,19,FGreater Manchester, she said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@LO]yD@POUyD@\O]zD@YOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
