PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782150512
OL,3,CGreens name councillor as candidate to
OL,4,Creplace Burnham as Manchester mayor
OL,6,FIn her speech to supporters, she said:
OL,7,F"As your Green mayor, I will
OL,8,Fprioritise people and planet over
OL,9,Fprofits. I will work for those who are
OL,10,Fstruggling to make ends meet and to
OL,11,Fget our high streets buzzing again.
OL,13,F"I will push back on a broken housing
OL,14,Fsystem that is designed to maximise
OL,15,Fprofits, instead of giving people the
OL,16,Fhomes they need, I will go further and
OL,17,Ffaster to get us the world class
OL,18,Ftransport system that we deserve here,
OL,19,Fand one that works for all our
OL,20,Fboroughs, not just for the centre.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
